product_name: The North Face Tannen Tote Bag - Women's - 2013 Closeout
long_description: Drop your 13 in. laptop into the main compartment of The North Face Tannen Tote Bag, snap your yoga mat under the hidden bungee cords at the top, and you're ready for work and play. External pockets hold your phone and water bottle. Internal organizational sleeve with silicone-backed elastic holds your USB flash drive and small personal items. Crafted of durable twill fabric with a waterproof coating to keep your gear dry. The North Face Tannen Tote Bag zips closed at the top for security. Closeout.
